          "data": {
            "children": [
              {
                "data": {
                  "value": "The filter is computed by applying the edge weights along one dimension and the smoothing weights along all other dimensions. If no axis is given, or a tuple of axes is given the filter is computed along all axes in turn, and the magnitude is computed as the square root of the average square magnitude of all the axes."
